description: Sets the active model version for a given machine learning model.

parameters.name: ModelName
parameters.description: The name of the machine learning model for which the active model version is being set.

parameters.name: ModelVersion
parameters.description: The version of the machine learning model for which the active model version is being set.

nested_items.name: ModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the machine learning model for which the active model version was set.

nested_items.name: ModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the machine learning model for which the active model version was set.

nested_items.name: CurrentActiveVersion
nested_items.description: The version that is currently active of the machine learning model for which the active model version was set.

nested_items.name: PreviousActiveVersion
nested_items.description: The previous version that was active of the machine learning model for which the active model version was set.

nested_items.name: CurrentActiveVersionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the machine learning model version that is the current active model version.

nested_items.name: PreviousActiveVersionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the machine learning model version that was the previous active model version.
